function.name: search_data_presence
function.description: Analyzes a transformer test report pages to detect if actual test data sections are present for oil testing, turns ratio, and winding resistance test.

Oil Testing.description: Respond 'Yes' only if structured data for oil testing is present; otherwise, respond 'No'.

Turns Ratio.description: Respond 'Yes' only if structured data for turns ratio testing is present; otherwise, respond 'No'.

Winding Resistance.description: Respond 'Yes' only if structured data for winding resistance is present; otherwise, respond 'No'.

Winding Tan Delta & Capacitance.description: Respond 'Yes' only if structured data for tan delta capacitance is present; otherwise, respond 'No'.
